# crabtunes

A **_WIP_** cross-platform music library manager built with Rust, inspired by applications like MusicBee and iTunes.

## TODO / GOALS

- [ ] Library Management
  - [ ] Scan local folders for music files (MP3, FLAC, OGG, etc.).
  - [ ] Read and edit metadata (tags) using a library like lofty.
  - [ ] Display music in a filterable, sortable library view (by artist, album, genre, etc.).
  - [ ] Display album art.
- [ ] Tag Editor
  - [ ] Make an extensible autotag feature that pulls tags from different sources.
- [ ] GUI
  - [ ] Make a GUI for the application with either Iced or Relm4
- [ ] Cross-Platform Support


